Title: An Act Changing the Name of New Argao Primary School in the Municipality of Malita, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Isidro Geverola Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 759
An Act Changing the Name of New Argao Primary School in the Municipality of Malita, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Isidro Geverola Primary School
Section 1. The name of the New Argao Primary School in the Municipality of Malita, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Isidro Geverola Primary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
